    <section class="my-4">
<div class="py-4"></div>
<h3 class="text-center">eNompilo-Pharmacy</h3>
<p>
  Our state of the art pharmacy gaurantees the well being of the community, for you and the one's you love.<br>
  Our friendly pharmicists are available to answer any questions or concerns you may have regarding over the counter medications as well as assisting you with your prescriptions.
  <ul>
    <li>We make sure over the counter items are always stocked.</li>
    <li>We are able to make special orders for medication that is needed for our clients which will be made available the next business day.</li>
    <li>At eNompilo-Pharmacy we strive for customer satisfaction we achieve this through a pharmacy club card that allows customers a percentage off on their medication.<br>
    if the medication is not covered you will be provided with an itemized receipt, which you will have to submit on your own.</li>
    <li>We accept cash, cheque, Medical aid, Discovery, Mastercard, Visa at our respective Pharmacies.</li>
</ul>
<b>Just a reminder:</b> Please make sure that you bring your Medical-Aid card or your Pharmacy club card as well as a form of ID when picking up prescriptions.
</p>
</section>

<hr>

<section class="my-4">
<div class="py-4"></div>
<h3 class="text-center">Hours of Operation</h3>
<p> <b>Weekdays</b><br>
  9 am to 8 pm, Monday through Friday<br>
     <b>Weekends</b><br>
     9 am to 1 pm, Saturdays and Sundays
</p>
</section>

<hr>

<section class="my-4">
