<h3 class="text-center">Pharmacy Refill Number</h3>
<p> <b>Contact Number:</b>1234567890
</p>
</section>
<hr>

<P>Please inform us at anytime if you have any information that changes in Address, Phone Number or Medical-Aid.</p>

  <a href="https://medlineplus.gov/druginformation.html" target="_blank">Information on Medications A-Z</a>

<hr>

<section class="my-4">
<div class="py-4"></div>
<h3 class="text-center">Pharmacy Medical-Aid Scheme</h3>
<p>eNompilo-Healthcare pharmacies participate in several Medical-Aid programs, when arriving for a presription or over the counter pickup,<br>
 please provide the your pharmacist with your Medical-Aid card so they can verify with your Medical-Aid provider if they cover set prescription/medication.<br>
 <br>
Some Medical-Aid schemes do not allow for out-of-area pharmacies to submit claims through Medical-Aid.<br>
<br>
In Cases where we can not work through your Medical-Aid provider we will issue you with an itemized receipt in which you can pay Cash, Check, Mastercard or Visa.
</P>
</section>
    
